---
title: Smoky Paprika Turkey & Potato Hash with Garlic Aioli & Pickled Red Onion
description: Spanish-style potatoes make for an irresistible hash that’s perfect any time of day! You’ll brown ground turkey with our chorizo-spiced paprika blend and toss with potatoes for a seriously satisfying skillet. Drizzle with cumin-spiced salsa brava and garlicky aioli and top with tangy pickled onion to bring it all together.
